msgctxt "1344"
msgid "Tanimura"
msgstr "Tanimura"

msgctxt "1348"
msgid "Katsuura"
msgstr "Katsuura"

msgctxt "1352"
msgid "Talk_Away"
msgstr "Talk_Away"

msgctxt "56_Tanimura"
msgid "26 years ago, you murdered a detective named Kaga, didn't you?"
msgstr "Hace 26 años, asesinaste a un detective llamado Kaga, ¿no es así?"

msgctxt "68_Katsuura"
msgid "And? What about it?"
msgstr "¿Y? ¿Qué tiene que ver eso?"

msgctxt "80_Tanimura"
msgid "He was one of your own, wasn't he? Why'd you have to kill\\r\n"\n"him over something so trivial as running away with the\\r\n"\n"woman he loved?"
msgstr "Él era uno de los tuyos, ¿no? ¿Por qué tuviste que matarlo\\r\n"\n"por algo tan simple como irse con la mujer que amaba?"

msgctxt "92_Katsuura"
msgid "Don't come any closer!"
msgstr "¡Aléjate de mí!"

msgctxt "104_Tanimura"
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr "¡Espera!"

